    "description": "Crystal Souls: Fragment Hunters is a top down indie space game where you shoot enemy ships, gather crystals, and upgrade your own ship.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou're a soldier aboard the Crystal Shark, tasked with finding and retrieving the mysterious missing crystals. You choose a level, after which it becomes a horde-survival game. As you survive the onslaught of enemy ships around you, you are able to collect the crystals you need.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe further you progress, the more items and ships you unlock.<br />\r\nThe longer you survive, the higher your rewards become.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEvery weapon and ship has its own pros and cons.<br />\r\nSome are more geared for long range, others short range.<br />\r\nExperiment and find a setup that you like.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAim at enemies, shoot enemies, pick up items, mine some ore, what more do you need?",
